 its characteristic\ntransient behaviour. Taken together, our analysis shows that this method is\nbroadly applicable to multistable dynamical systems and offers a powerful and\nefficient approach for understanding their behaviour.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 May 2020 18:53:02 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 3 Nov 2020 22:16:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-05"}
