e points motivate a\ndirect study of this effect on the cosmological parameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 10 May 2020 22:51:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2020 08:47:48 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-10-22"}
