 mechanism, such as a gas-rich merger\nor the presence of giant turbulent clumps, early in the history of its\nformation. Dynamical heating by minor mergers and radial migration may also\nplay roles in forming the current thick-disk structure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 May 2020 05:20:57 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 15 May 2020 09:12:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-17"}
