rarily, for the long positive temperature fluctuation events, the mean time\nscales remain roughly equal to the integral scales, irrespective of stability.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 May 2020 09:34:11 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 13 May 2020 19:27:12 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-07-30"}
