es, all intersection cohomology\noperations are induced by classical ones.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 11 May 2020 09:42:16 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 29 Jul 2020 08:51:53 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Tue, 14 Sep 2021 11:38:36 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-09-15"}
